- Who was it?

276
00:19:43,719 --> 00:19:45,103
Tell me who it was.

277
00:19:45,223 --> 00:19:48,135
I want to know who it was.
- I won't tell you who he was...

278
00:19:49,277 --> 00:19:50,892
but what he did.

279
00:19:51,012 --> 00:19:52,766
No...

280
00:19:53,213 --> 00:19:56,047
