341
00:24:03,927 --> 00:24:05,269
Very well.

342
00:24:05,852 --> 00:24:08,524
It's a precious relation, dear.

343
00:24:09,288 --> 00:24:11,160
Don't neglect it, it's important.

344
00:24:11,260 --> 00:24:13,900
